<body>

	<div class="intro" style="text-align:center">
		<img src="images/bicycle-icon.svg" style="margin-top:100px" height="200" />
		<div class="head-title">Cycle Fitness</div>
		<div class="links-bar">&middot; <a href="#" class="about-link">About</a> &middot; <a href="#" class="seminars-link">Seminars</a> &middot; <a href="#" class="events-link">Events</a> &middot; <a href="#" class="catalog-link">Catalog</a> &middot; <a href="#" class="faq-link">FAQ</a> &middot; <a href="#" class="contact-link">Contact</a> &middot; </div>
	</div>

	<div class="content-wrapper">
			<div class="pure-g">
				<div class="video-container">
					<div class="video-content-wrapper">
						<div class="video-title">Here at Cycle Fitness, we're geared for the pace of urban life.</div>
						<div class="video-subtitle">With an immense selection for all kinds of riders and unbeatable service, we're here to help you.</div>
						<div class="ui inverted button learn-more-button">Learn More</div>
					</div>
					<div class="video-overlay">
					</div>
          <div class="video-wrapper">
  					<video autoplay loop class="video">
  						<source src="res/videobg.mp4" type="video/mp4"/>
  						Your browser does not support the video tag. I suggest you upgrade your browser.
  					</video>
          </div>
					
					
			</div>
		</div>

	      <div class="about-qualities">
	        <div class="pure-g">
	          <div class="col-u-1">
	            <div class="features-wrapper">
	              <div class="pure-u-1-3 quality">
	                <div class="ic">
	                  <i class="icon heart shadow"></i>
	                </div>
	                <h2>Love</h2>
	                <p>Here at Cycle Fitness, we love what we do, and we want to bring that love to you, our customers. We have a fine selection of bikes to fit any kind of task, from fitness to commuting. We do what we love—by helping you do what you love.</p>
	              </div>
	              <div class="pure-u-1-3 quality">
	                <div class="ic">
	                  <i class="icon group shadow"></i>
	                </div>
	                <h2>Community</h2>
	                <p>We are one with the community at Cycle Fitness. From weekly seminars, to monthly cycling trips, we build connections that help our community flourish. Here at Cycle Fitness, we try our best to bring together our community one pedal at a time.</p>
	              </div>
	              <div class="pure-u-1-3 quality">
	                <div class="ic">
	                  <i class="icon wrench shadow"></i>
	                </div>
	                <h2>Passion</h2>
	                <p>We’ve been doing our job for decades, and we’re here to use our experience to help you find the best bike for your needs. Need a bike to coast down the sunny hills of Ithaca? We’ve got you. A bike to commute to work in the bustling streets of NYC? We’ve got you there too.</p>
	              </div>
	              <div class="clearfix"></div>
	            </div>
	          </div>
	        </div>
	      </div>

		<div class="social">

			<div class="social-title">
				A Bike Shop for the Community
			</div>

			<div class="social-subtitle">
